headline: Insulet Corporation (PODD): A Bull Case Theory
summary: We came across a bullish thesis on Insulet Corporation on The Wealth Dynasty Report’s Substack. In this article, we will summarize the bulls’ thesis on PODD. Insulet Corporation’s share was trading at $255.81 as of January 30st. PODD’s trailing and forward P/E were 74.37 and 41.84 respectively according to Yahoo Finance.
